data.description: Enjoy spacious living with a great room featuring cozy fireplace, formal dining with tray ceilings and charming built-ins.  Beautifully updated kitchen boasting quartz counter tops and tiled backsplash; stainless appliances including fridge and ample cabinets. Main bedroom is huge with luxurious ceiling and bath that offers separate tub and shower and walk-in closet.  Laundry room has extra cabinets.  Double garage, level lot for easy living, deck and big privacy fenced yard.  Perfect for relaxing or entertaining.  Don't miss out!  Agents see remarks for showing.
